      //   FWS     =   ([*WSP CRLF] 1*WSP) /  obs-FWS
      //                                   ; Folding white space

      // But note the erratum:
      // http://www.rfc-editor.org/errata_search.php?rfc=5322&eid=1908:
      //   In the obsolete syntax, any amount of folding white space MAY be
